[The 7 new outbreaks covered above in OIE follow-up report no 3 are backyard holdings, detected due to the surveillance undertaken by Cyprus veterinary services in response to the virulent outbreak; 5 of them, like the previous 7, are located in Lefkosia; 2 infected backyard holdings (outbreaks 1 & 12) are located in Paphos.

For additional information on NCD, see http://www.oie.int/fileadmin/Home/eng/Health_standards/tahm/2.03.14_NEWCASTLE_DIS.pdf.

A summarising OIE report on NCD in Cyprus, with accumulated data and a map showing the locations of the outbreaks is available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/temp/reports/en_fup_0000013741_20130709_174941.pdf. - Mod.AS]
